total of Pounds 85m was raised in conjunction with three other Kleinwort
Benson managed investment trusts.
Revenue for the six months to May 31 came to Pounds 3.43m (Pounds 3.8m) and
earnings per share worked through at 2.2p (2.42p). The interim dividend is
unchanged at 1.25p.
