The introduction costs would be fully depreciated during the present year,
Mr Philip Meeson, chairman, assured shareholders.
Earnings per share came to 7.5p (9.4p). The final dividend is 2p, for a
maintained 3.3p total.
For the current year there were indications of improved performance, and
