FT  18 JUN 93 / UK Company News: Tighter margins hit Dart
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
TIGHTER MARGINS in aviation services and the cost of introducing Electra
freighters into European service hit the profit of Dart Group.
In the year ended March 31 1993 it lifted turnover from Pounds 37.4m to
