FT  18 JUN 93 / World News in Brief: Duke banned
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Duke of Hamilton, 54, was banned from driving for eight years, put on
probation and ordered to do 200 hours' community service. He had admitted a
fifth drink-driving offence, assaulting police and dangerous driving.
